1xAuthenticator is only available to registered customers.

When something important happens on your account, for example, you change your password or withdraw funds, and we need to be sure it's really you doing this, 1xAuthenticator generates a single-use verification code.

We send the code to you in a push notification, and all you have to do is enter it in the confirmation field - this is much quicker, more convenient and more secure than sending it by SMS.

A history of these actions will be available in this section.

Код пришлём вам в виде Push-уведомления, останется ввести его в поле для подтверждения - это быстрее, удобнее и безопаснее, чем обычные СМС.
